  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/6cfc85ad0bcdf258282aa151aee086e2.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/6cfc85ad0bcdf258282aa151aee086e2.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/6cfc85ad0bcdf258282aa151aee086e2.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Collect devastating power-ups and unleash chaos on your opponents to claim the crown!</strong><br><br><strong>Touch</strong> your opponents when you are <strong>invulnerable </strong>or <strong>escape</strong> if they are!<br><br>Trick your opponents using a combination of <strong>skill-based movement</strong> and <strong>powerups</strong> to reach the <strong>crown</strong> in <strong>special levels</strong>!<br><br>Dodge <strong>deadly lasers</strong> and precarious ledges to stay in the game - <strong>quick reflexes</strong> are key to victory!<br><br>Be careful which <strong>buttons</strong> you touch - some hold <strong>surprises</strong> that can help or destroy you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/9f5d907a15939f62d7809d7e15c5245c.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/9f5d907a15939f62d7809d7e15c5245c.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/9f5d907a15939f62d7809d7e15c5245c.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenge your <strong>friends</strong> or <strong>AI</strong> opponents in <strong>thrilling and chaotic PVP battles</strong> up to <strong>4</strong> players<br></li><li><strong>Unleash</strong> a barrage of explosive power-ups, including <strong>bombs, rockets, mines, and turrets</strong><br></li><li><strong>Become smaller, faster and invisible</strong> to avoid your opponents or strike them<br></li><li><strong>Strike</strong> your enemies when you have the <strong>yellow glow</strong> and <strong>dodge</strong> their assaults when they have the upper hand<br></li><li>Reach the <strong>crown</strong> in some <strong>special levels</strong> to <strong>win</strong> instantly the round<br></li><li>Disable weapon power-ups and challenge your friends in a <strong>peaceful gameplay mode</strong><br></li><li><strong>60</strong> unique <strong>levels </strong>with explosive <strong>surprises</strong>, <strong>lasers</strong>, <strong>buttons</strong> and <strong>bombs</strong><br></li><li><strong>Physics-Based movement</strong>, watch out to fall down!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>NOTE: If you have problems with controller in game, just disable all controllers in Steam Big Picture</strong>",
