e your <strong>friends</strong> or <strong>AI</strong> opponents in <strong>thrilling and chaotic PVP battles</strong> up to <strong>4</strong> players<br></li><li><strong>Unleash</strong> a barrage of explosive power-ups, including <strong>bombs, rockets, mines, and turrets</strong><br></li><li><strong>Become smaller, faster and invisible</strong> to avoid your opponents or strike them<br></li><li><strong>Strike</strong> your enemies when you have the <strong>yellow glow</strong> and <strong>dodge</strong> their assaults when they have the upper hand<br></li><li>Reach the <strong>crown</strong> in some <strong>special levels</strong> to <strong>win</strong> instantly the round<br></li><li>Disable weapon power-ups and challenge your friends in a <strong>peaceful gameplay mode</strong><br></li><li><strong>60</strong> unique <strong>levels </strong>with explosive <strong>surprises</strong>, <strong>lasers</strong>, <strong>buttons</strong> and <strong>bombs</strong><br></li><li><strong>Physics-Based movement</strong>, watch out to fall down!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.poster.avif?t=1737373356\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.webm?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344450/extras/c0014132231f436fb0b7e2017ce824a0.mp4?t=1737373356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>NOTE: If you have problems with controller in game, just disable all controllers in Steam Big Picture</strong>",
